getDataVersion.comment: Fetches the Data Version of the Server.

getId.comment: Fetches the Unique Identifier of this Server's Version, as a trimmed UUID string.

getName.comment: Fetches the Friendly Name of this Server's Version, such as "1.20.2".

getProtocolVersion.comment: Fetches the Protocol Version of this Server.

params.name: packType
params.comment: The type of pack to get the version of.

getPackVersion.comment: Fetches the Resource or Data Pack Version of this Server, depending on the input type of `PackType`.

getBuildTime.comment: Fetches the Time this server version was built from source.

isStable.comment: Whether this Server Version is considered stable.
